race.comment: BELLA GEORGIA (7) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (20.53) in a Grade 5 at Capalaba. The form from her last run stacks up well. Has ability and is a key runner. GYPSY KING (4) turned in a moderate run last time when fifth at this track over 520m behind Some Diva (30.96) in a Grade 5. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. WHISPERING ABBEY (1) showed good pace from out wide and was prominent early but began to paddle and faded out of it when 6th at this track in Mix 5 company. Has ability and is one of the better chances. PRINCESS DARCY (2) cannot be written off despite a miss here at her latest outing.
